featureType.title: Australian Depth Contours (MERI zones)
featureType.abstract: Depth contours for 30, 70, 200, 700, 2000, 4000 and 6000m corresponding with the Parks Australia common language Ecosystem depth zones for MERI reporting. Contours derived from the Australian Bathymetric and Topography Grid, June 2009 (Geoscience Australia) by the Australian Hydrographic Service. Styled for use on the Seamap Australia website.
